<font color=#A5FA7D>아야야야
<SYNC Start=2711252><P Class=KRCC>
<font color=#A5FA7D>아빠
<SYNC Start=2711726><P Class=KRCC>
<font color=#A5FA7D>아빠가...
<SYNC Start=2713533><P Class=KRCC>
<font color=#A5FA7D>엄마, 무슨 일이야?
<SYNC Start=2715201><P Class=KRCC>
<font color=#A5FA7D>아빠가 말야...<br>아빠가...
<SYNC Start=2719388><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2723922><P Class=KRCC>
<font color=#A5FA7D>기다려!
<SYNC Start=2725872><P Class=KRCC>
<font color=#A5FA7D>젠장...
<SYNC Start=2728004><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2731070><P Class=KRCC>
아버지가...
<SYNC Start=2733062><P Class=KRCC>
